{"TopicId":149519,"ForumId":70,"TopicTitle":"PC hard crashes (shuts down) after installing graphics mods","CreatedByName":"Feral Guyute","CreatedById":131640,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-08T21:24:25Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Feral Guyute","CreatedById":131640,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-08T21:24:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust installed some graphical mods (stock visual enhancements, and scatterer) and now game restarts my pc after a few seconds when playing. It worked fine before the mods. I have a R9 290 x gpu, 16 gigs of ram an I-5-4440 CPU and a HIVE 80 plus Bronze 650 W PSU. Any suggestions?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DrLicor","CreatedById":165712,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-11T09:10:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHave a look at \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/83212-how-to-get-support-read-first/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ethis thread\u003C/a\u003E, it\u0027s helps us to detect what\u0027s going wrong.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTry to run it in \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/95837-forcing-directx11-40-memory-reduction/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Edx-11 mode\u003C/a\u003E or \u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oJcFqNnyjmQ\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Eopen-gl\u003C/a\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, how did you install them?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nanddd, welcome to the forums \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-10-11T09:11:12Z\u0022 title=\u002210/11/2016 09:11  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 11, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by DrLicor\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ser","CreatedById":104207,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-11T09:51:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222793744\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022149519\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475961865\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022131640\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Feral Guyute\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 10/9/2016 at 0:24 AM, Feral Guyute said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust installed some graphical mods (stock visual enhancements, and scatterer) and now game restarts my pc after a few seconds when playing. It worked fine before the mods. I have a R9 290 x gpu, 16 gigs of ram an I-5-4440 CPU and a HIVE 80 plus Bronze 650 W PSU. Any suggestions?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLooks like a shader processor or a graphic driver issue. Do other games (graphic demanding) run well on your system?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Freds","CreatedById":132437,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-11T12:32:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe your pc is overheating ....\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Feral Guyute","CreatedById":131640,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-24T01:45:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI installed a different version of the graphical mod and the crashes stop. I don\u0027t know what went on with the old one. The way i installed them was to extract the files into the game data folder\u00A0(I think this is the folder). Also My PC runs other games fine at high settings like the witcher 3 and and MGS V both work 100% fine with the graphics beefed up all the way. Also there is no way it is over 